Cannot be Special Summoned from the Deck. You can Tribute Summon (but not Set) this card by Tributing 1 Dinosaur-Type monster. Once per turn: You can change this card to face-down Defense Position. When this card is Flip Summoned: Change all other monsters to face-down Defense Position. If your opponent attacks this card, any battle damage they take is doubled.
